Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost, let’s start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really happy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you're always meeting\Nto someone's expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you change to\Nwho you really wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you always have a great smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of only “the beginning,”\NI wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and someday, I'll live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:01:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, precious things are never in shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what it is\Nwhen you get it or lose it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost,\Nlet's start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn’t lower your guard, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll bury you and correct\Nold mistakes, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you do now, it’s too late…\NI’ve won…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Leaf Village will crumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the man who carried on the Leaf Will\Nof the First and Second Hokages…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru! Now I will perform an\Nace Jutsu that even you don’t know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! Sealing Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden Secret Technique:\NReaper Death Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Jutsu I don’t know…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must hurry…\NThis darkness is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have you show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to be killed\Nslowly by your predecessors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please perform that Jutsu, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like…I was just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?\NYou’re already stumbling…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all that’s left…\Nis to catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness has disappeared…\NWhat’s this Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarutobi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry…Sarutobi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We caused you trouble…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord First Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Second Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your own subordinates…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All members in\Nthe Leaf Village are a part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers believe in me,\Nand I believe in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what the Hokage is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saru… Protect those who love\Nthe village and believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And bring them up as individuals\Nto whom you can leave the next era.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of tomorrow, you are the…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toying with even the lives\Nof your own subordinates…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subordinates’ lives?\NStop the endless nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t these kids believed in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Enma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Striking Shadow Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it! You little--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this sensation…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Die! 					– Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hold them off here somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't our back-up here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is out of our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Summoning!\NBring Down the House Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Jutsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Ibiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, is that body\Nthe only thing that grew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Jiraiya…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiraiya…! One of Sannin,\Nthe three legendary Shinobi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeps, open up those little eyes\Nof yours just this once and observe well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The devil region beyond heaven\Nof Jiraiya, the fantastic sage Ninja…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snakes that have been antagonized\Nby the frog. Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that Orochimaru has finally started, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s the Third Hokage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Exam arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t die…old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…didn’t you dodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Reaper Death Seal…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this Sealing Jutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in exchange for the effectiveness\Nof Jutsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one’s own soul is handed over\Nto the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a Jutsu that costs your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Jutsu doesn’t activate…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no need to dodge.\NI will die, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time the Sealing ends,\Nmy soul will also be devoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a Jutsu of the hero\Nwho once saved this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now, you will also die…\Nby this Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this Jutsu also sealed\Nthat Nine-Tailed Fox, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, your soul will be dragged out…\Nand sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body…won’t listen to what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll probably be able to see it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul is also already\Nabout halfway out, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have their souls sealed\Nby this Jutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will suffer inside the belly\Nof the Grim Reaper for eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and will never attain peace…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who seal and are sealed\Nhave their souls intertwined,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and will hate each other,\Nand continue to battle for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is… the Grim Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off! You old dotard!\NI won’t let you do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and…die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone. Line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konohamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konohamaru, it’s not going\Nto collapse, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll…it’ll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The structure of this face rock path is old,\Nbut is of strong construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa said so before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it’ll definitely be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone’s coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uchiha, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about Temari?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t run away like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be your opponent this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed you’d been\Ncreamed by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you’re okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Somehow…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it didn’t turn out to\Nbe much of a delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it’s time necessary for\NGaara’s recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it’ll lead to\Nhis consumption of Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shampoo, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it’s Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are several smells near him.\NHe caught up…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s totally stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to fight with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this clump of countless smells\Ncoming from another direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There’s something besides us\Ntracking Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy? An ally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know. But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Kankuro! I’ll take him again…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Temari, you take Gaara\Nand go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re at your limit…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t need a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped…\NI’ll be your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! I don’t care who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shino?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put a female beetle on you\Nbefore you left the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The females have almost no smell…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a male can sniff out\Nthe subtle smell of the female.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the male itself\Nhas a strong smell…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke Uchiha…\NYou pursue Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the battle between you\Nand him hasn’t been settled yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll fight him, because originally\NI was his opponent…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I withdraw!\NPlease go ahead with the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me here! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re very confident.\NBut are you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go back you up if\NI have just ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. By then, I’ll be done too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of you know anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys probably don’t know\Nof the real terror of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case…\Nyou’ll teach me that terror?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you defeat me and chase Gaara,\Nyou’ll be forced to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, only if you can defeat me.
